729902f-a.title: Richmond: White Plains Avenue - Bell Street
729902f-a.text:
White Plains Ave., east side, (background, houses thereon), at the head of Bell Street (Rosebank). The view is eastward on Bell Street and includes the house (right) that occupies the S.W. corner of the two streets. White Plains Ave. was formerly Charles Street.
July 12, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
